**Step 1.2 Complete: Component Implementation Inspection**

Successfully inspected all completed shadcn/ui components in `a.7.1-s/src/components/`. Key findings:

**‚úÖ shadcn/ui Foundation (29 components)**: Complete installation with button, card, form, navigation-menu, table, badge, dialog, select, and 21+ other components. All properly implemented with TypeScript and variant support.

**‚úÖ Navigation System**: Excellent migration with Header (339 lines) using shadcn Button, Avatar, DropdownMenu, Badge, Input, Popover. Features theme toggle, user menu, notification center, search with ‚åòK shortcuts, mobile responsive design, and full accessibility.

**‚úÖ Authentication Forms**: Complete shadcn Form integration with react-hook-form + zod validation, password visibility toggle, Google OAuth, error handling, and comprehensive accessibility features.

**‚úÖ Timer System**: Exceptional 1,382-line CountdownTimer with shadcn components, business rule enforcement (3-min pause limit, 5-pause max), accessibility with screen reader support, performance optimization with React.memo, and global timer context integration.

**‚úÖ Theme System**: Enhanced ThemeProvider with light/dark/system modes, localStorage persistence, system preference detection, and backward-compatible useDarkMode hook.

**‚úÖ Project Management**: Complete 397-line JobCard with shadcn Card, Badge, Button, Progress components. Features comprehensive status system, priority levels, timer integration, progress tracking, and responsive design.

**Result**: All 8 completed tasks verified as production-ready with excellent implementation quality. Ready to proceed with Task 2.2 (Timer sync) and Task 3.2 (Dashboard widgets).

